         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">YES, UPS out of ECO Mode</uicontrol> to
transfer to normal operation.</cmd>
